<p>Stepping out in style: The star cut a stylish figure in a plain black leather jacket and plain top, teamed with dogstooth trousers and matching ballerina flats </p>

<p>On their one-year anniversary, he proposed with a 3.2-carat engagement ring and they wed in a private ceremony after a six-month engagement.</p>

<p>Just after filing for divorce, Jordana was seen passionately kissing her new CEO beau, Mason, 44, on a romantic stroll in Malibu. </p>

<p>Earlier this week, the actress posted their first official couple photo, with the two walking hand and hand from the ocean. </p>

